or Reporting\r\nâ€¢  Escrow origination and servicing\r\nâ€¢  Rate Lock\r\nâ€¢  FASB 91\r\nâ€¢  Collateral revaluation and maintenance of collateral history\r\nâ€¢  Generation  of  a  quote/key  facts  illustration  from  the  Loan  Origination  System  and  the  Loan  Maintenance\r\nSystem\r\nâ€¢  Integration of Finanz Tools with the Loan Origination System in CRM\r\nâ€¢  Dormancy Status for Non-Financial Transactions\r\nâ€¢  Changing the behaviour of the menu option, HLACAM, which performs the amortization batch job\r\nâ€¢  Validation at the time of rephasement, keeping the EMI fixed and changing the tenor\r\nâ€¢  Carryover of charge demands\r\nâ€¢  Overflow carryover\r\nâ€¢  EMI plus interest on holiday period to be raised as a combined demand at the time of the first instalment\r\nâ€¢  Enabling  scheduled  and  unscheduled  loan  repayments  and  loan  disbursement  for  forward  contract\r\nutilization\r\nâ€¢  Accepting cheque for scheduled and unscheduled loan repayment and loan payoff\r\nâ€¢  Dropping of multiple disbursement parameter\r\nâ€¢  Securitization: Pool creation criteria based on geographic location of the mortgaged property\r\nâ€¢  Handling of minor's accounts\r\nâ€¢  Display of the portion of permitted annual overpayment used in a calendar year\r\nâ€¢  Analysis of cross-functional dependency of retail loans module on payment systems\r\nâ€¢  Calculation and display of Annual Percentage Rate (APR) as per CCA guideline for UK market\r\nâ€¢  Calculation and display of APR for loans having a subsidy amount\r\nâ€¢  Minimum balance check for automatic debits\r\n\r\nPROJECT\r\nPrice Waterhouse Coopers, New York - Onsite project for US market study, gap analysis, business\r\nrequirement gathering and developing functional requirement specifications\r\n\r\nAuthored the following requirement specifications for enhancements in Finacle:\r\n\r\nâ€¢  Mortgage (including Buydown) Origination and Servicing\r\nâ€¢  Investor Reporting\r\nâ€¢  Special Products- Adjustable Rate Mortgages (ARMs), Construction loans, Balloon loans\r\nâ€¢  Escrow Servicing for Mortgages and Liability accounts\r\nâ€¢  Impound Accounts, Buydowns and Buyups\r\nâ€¢  Liability (DDA accounts) Origination and Servicing\r\nâ€¢  Line Of Credit Origination (HELOC, PLOC, RELOC) and Servicing\r\nâ€¢  Personal Line of Credit Origination and Servicing\r\nâ€¢  Origination and Servicing of Boat Loans, Personal Loans and Auto Loans\r\nâ€¢  General Ledger\r\nâ€¢  Basel II Data Capture\r\nâ€¢  Minor Accounts\r\n\r\nWHITE PAPER\r\nâ€¢   Authored a white paper on \"Credit Ratings-Empty Rituals\"",
